BUILDING ELECTRICAL DISTRIBUTION
====================================

Main Distribution Points:
- Main Switchboard: Level 0 (Basement L2)
- Sub-boards: 13 total (1 per floor + lobby)
- Emergency Generator: Basement level, 1500kW capacity
- UPS System: Server room, 500kW backup

Lighting Network:
- LED Luminaires: ~4500 total units
- Control: DALI dimming system
- Emergency Lighting: Battery backup 3-hour autonomy
- Occupancy Sensors: 847 zones (one per room)

Power Distribution:
- Main Incoming: 2000A, 400V 3-phase
- Floor Distribution: Variable per occupancy
- Data Cabling: Cat 6A throughout
- WiFi Access Points: 150 units (WiFi 6)

Safety Systems:
- Fire Alarm: Category A (fully automatic)
- Emergency Exits: LED signage + manual call points
- RCD Protection: All circuits
- Backup Power: 48-hour generator fuel supply

Circuit Schedule:
- Lighting Circuits: 156 total
- Power Circuits: 234 total
- Special Circuits: 45 total (HVAC, lifts, etc.)
- Data Circuits: 320 total

Cable Routing:
- Main riser: Backbone conduit 4" diameter
- Floor distribution: Under-floor cable trays
- Vertical risers: Every core zone (4 locations)
- Accessible everywhere for maintenance

Compliance Status:
- AS/NZS 3000 Compliant: YES
- REC Certificate: REC-001847 (valid 2027)
- Electrical Safety Office: Certified
- Inspection Status: PASSED

